# The presence of this .npmignore makes npm ignore the sibling .gitignore for
# packing. The frontend third-party references (references/design/*.md and
# references/ui-ux-db/**) are gitignored because they are materialized from the
# upstreams/ submodules at build/prepack time, but they MUST ship in the npm
# tarball and Codex marketplace bundle. By NOT listing those paths here, they are
# included in the package. Keep this file minimal so the materialized refs pack.

# OS / editor junk that must never ship.
.DS_Store
